OL,3,CBrianna Ghey's mum says school phone
OL,4,Cban 'would have really helped' daughter
OL,6,FThe mother of murdered teenager
OL,7,FBrianna Ghey says a school phone ban
OL,8,Fwould really have helped her daughter,
OL,9,Fas she launches a campaign for a
OL,10,Fstatutory ban in schools.
OL,12,FEsther Ghey is calling on the
OL,13,FGovernment to provide funding to
OL,14,Fschools for pouches to lock phones in
OL,15,Fduring the school day.
OL,17,FShe success at Brianna's old school,
OL,18,FBirchwood Community High in Warrington.
OL,20,F"For me, it would have really helped
OL,21,FBrianna," Ms Ghey said.
