OL,3,CBrianna Ghey's mum says school phone
OL,4,Cban 'would have really helped' daughter
OL,6,F"It would have helped her to focus on
OL,7,Fher school work. She wouldn't have
OL,8,Fbeen getting in to so much trouble
OL,9,Fbecause all of the issues were around
OL,10,Fthe phone use.
OL,12,F"She would have had a much better
OL,13,Fchance in life. She would have been
OL,14,Fable to focus on her education. She
OL,15,Fwould have been able to make friends
OL,16,Fwith her peers.
OL,18,F"And I think that schools, parents and
OL,19,Fchildren need support from Government,
OL,20,Fbecause this issue is just too big for
OL,21,Fanybody to handle on their own."
