OL,3,CBrianna Ghey's mum says school phone
OL,4,Cban 'would have really helped' daughter
OL,6,FDuring the three years Brianna was at
OL,7,FBirchwood, there were 120 safeguarding
OL,8,Flogs and 116 behaviour logs around her
OL,9,Fphone use, Ms Ghey said.
OL,11,F"These ranged from Brianna being at
OL,12,Frisk of child sexual exploitation, to
OL,13,Fwhat she was accessing online, that
OL,14,Fwas encouraging her to self harm and
OL,15,Fto have an eating disorder," she said.
OL,17,F"As a parent, I really felt like I was
OL,18,Ffailing," Ms Ghey added. "I didn't
OL,19,Fknow what to do."
