OL,3,CBrianna Ghey's mum says school phone
OL,4,Cban 'would have really helped' daughter
OL,6,FUnder the former Conservative
OL,7,Fgovernment, schools were issued non-
OL,8,Fstatutory guidance intending to stop
OL,9,Fthe use of phones during the school
OL,10,Fday.
OL,12,FMs Ghey has launched an open letter to
OL,13,FEducation Secretary Bridget Phillipson
OL,14,Fand Prime Minister Sir Keir Starmer
OL,15,Fcalling for a statutory ban that would
OL,16,Fsee pupils unable to access their
OL,17,Fphones for the entire school day,
OL,18,Funless they are exempt for medical or
OL,19,Faccessibility reasons.
