OL,6,FMs Ghey said the school also has
OL,7,Fdetection measures to ensure children
OL,8,Fare not bringing in a second phone,
OL,9,Fand uses Velcro pouches for children
OL,10,Fwith health conditions or who are
OL,11,Fyoung carers.
OL,13,F"The funding needs to be in place,
OL,14,Fbecause I've spoken to headteachers,
OL,15,Fand they've said sometimes it's a
OL,16,Fchoice between a new classroom
OL,17,Fassistant or the pouches, and
OL,18,Fheadteachers shouldn't have to make
OL,19,Fthat choice," Ms Ghey said.
