OL,3,CBrianna Ghey's mum says school phone
OL,4,Cban 'would have really helped' daughter
OL,6,F"And I think that's the issue with
OL,7,Fschools, because there's so many
OL,8,Fparents that are completely locking
OL,9,Fdown phone or that are choosing to
OL,10,Fgive the children brick phones so they
OL,11,Fcan't access social media, but when
OL,12,Fthey go to secondary school they're
OL,13,Fopened up to a world of harms because
OL,14,Fall the children have phones."
OL,16,FA ban in schools is just "one part of
OL,17,Fthe puzzle" in the approach to
OL,18,Fchildren's phone and social media
OL,19,Fusage, she added.
